      "title": "EgoLink Bench",
      "content": "EgoLink 2026 evaluation benchmark for egocentric social reasoning.\n\nRegistration\nMake sure to use the same e-mail address and teamname in the EgoLink 2026, we will manually add users who can submit results based on the email addresses and teamname registered with EgoLink 2026.\n\nSubmit your result and check the scores\nMake sure your submitted zip file as following directory structure:\n\n|submission.zip\n\n||--predictions.jsonl\n\nThe predictions.jsonl file follows the following format:\n\n{\"id\": \"\\<id\\>\", \"answer\": \"\\<your_answer\\>\"}\n\nOne example:\n\n{\"id\": \"Eval_4020\", \"answer\": \"Casual friendliness with lighthearted teasing\"}",
